description:

author: National Geographic
description:
Hundreds of students learn magic at the College of Magic in Cape Town, South Africa, and @DavidBlaine is teaching them one particular trick that'll fool even the world's best magicians.

All episodes of David Blaine: Do Not Attempt are now streaming on Disney+ and Hulu.
title: Students have been learning magic here for over 40 years #DavidBlaineDoNotAttempt
